        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>I know that things are not the same </l>
          <l>I guess you’ll have </l>
          <l>to understand </l>
          <l>You get it so wrong </l>
          <l>Those things are messing-up my head </l>
          <l>But I </l>
          <l>still act like I don’t care </l>
          <l>Just want to see you smile again</l>
